<h3 class="bold">Video Example(s):</h3>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="376uxh" data-video-descrip="Possibly the most well-known thing about this show are the cards with sound effects that appeared when someone landed a big hit. This was primarily introduced as a cost-cutting measure and to cover up some of the fight scenes." data-video-title="1960s Batman" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/376uxh_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/376uxh.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HitFlash" data-video-tropename="Hit Flash" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="7" data-video-media-sources="Series/Batman1966" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
