</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">1960s Batman</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Possibly the most well-known thing about this show are the cards with sound effects that appeared when someone landed a big hit. This was primarily introduced as a cost-cutting measure and to cover up some of the fight scenes. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>The Hit Flash</span> </h3>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
