<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">1960s Batman</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Possibly the most well-known thing about this show are the cards with sound effects that appeared when someone landed a big hit. This was primarily introduced as a cost-cutting measure and to cover up some of the fight scenes.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="376uxh">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
<p>How well does it match the trope?</p>
